Package Order

Class OrderInvoice

  • java.lang.Object
    • Order.OrderInvoice
  • public class OrderInvoice
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents an order invoice of an order. Each OrderInvoice is created from an Order.
    Author:
    Glenda Hong Zixuan

      • getTotalPrice

        public float getTotalPrice​(boolean calc)
        Gets the total price of this OrderInvoice.
        Parameters:
        calc - If calc is true, the getTotalPrice method will recalculate the total price, set the totalPrice field of this OrderInvoice to the recalculated price, and then return the recalculated price.
        Otherwise, the getTotalPrice returns the value stored in the totalPrice field of this OrderInvoice.
        Returns:
        the total price of this OrderInvoice.

      • getTaxDetails

        public float[] getTaxDetails​(float gst,
                             float serviceCharge)
        Gets the tax details of this OrderInvoice.
        Parameters:
        gst - The GST tax as a decimal value.
        serviceCharge - The service tax as a decimal value.
        Returns:
        the tax details of this OrderInvoice in a float array of size 4.
         The first element is the total price without taxes.
         The second element is the total price including GST tax.
         The third element is the total price including service tax.
         The fourth element is the total price with taxes.
